OL,9,     GChiara returns to her Italian
OL,10,     Groots as Dec jokes and Gary gets
OL,11,     Gflustered playing with Emily.
OL,12,G1410FFour in a Bed
OL,13,     GThe first visit of the week is to
OL,14,     GThe Lazy Pug in Warwickshire, run
OL,15,     Gby best friends Ash and Rosie,
OL,16,     Gwhere the quirky decor and neon
OL,17,     Glighting give some of the guests
OL,18,     Ga headache.
