OL,4,G1440FFour in a Bed
OL,5,     GThe B&Bers head to Cardiff to
OL,6,     Gstay at Crofts Hotel, run by chef
OL,7,     GLorraine. They're all expecting a
OL,8,     Gknockout breakfast, but uninvited
OL,9,     Gguests ruin things for some of
OL,10,     Gthem.
OL,11,G1510FFour in a Bed
OL,12,     GAnthony hosts the week's third
OL,13,     Gvisit at The Hollybush Inn, in
OL,14,     GWarwickshire. His 16th-century
OL,15,     Gcoaching inn wows the guests with
OL,16,     Gits history. But some think the
OL,17,     Gcleanliness needs updating.
