OL,4,G1540FFour in a Bed
OL,5,     GThe B&Bers go glamping in the
OL,6,     Gweek's last visit, at The Pretty
OL,7,     GThing glampsite in Essex. Ash and
OL,8,     GRosie embrace the luxe of their
OL,9,     GAztec tent before host Phil
OL,10,     Gserves his first-ever breakfast.
OL,11,G1615FFour in a Bed
OL,12,     GIt's payment day, and the B&Bers
OL,13,     Greconvene to feud about
OL,14,     Gfacilities, bicker over beds and
OL,15,     Gcross swords over sausages,
OL,16,     Gbefore the payments are revealed
OL,17,     Gand the winner is announced.
